  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to evaluate the evolution of quality of life and voice function
      with different questionnaires (VIH, SF36) before and after total thyroidectomy.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <overall_status>Completed</overall_status>
